higher brain living?

00:00:59.620 --> 00:01:04.550 align:middle line:84%
>>COTTON: Well, many years ago
I had a profound experience that

00:01:04.550 --> 00:01:07.180 align:middle line:84%
changed the entire
direction of my life.

00:01:07.180 --> 00:01:10.800 align:middle line:84%
