almost disabling headaches.

00:01:19.310 --> 00:01:21.480 align:middle line:84%
And I was in and out
doctor's offices.

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:24.030 align:middle line:90%
And nobody could ever help me.

00:01:24.030 --> 00:01:27.230 align:middle line:84%
And I just kind of fumbled
my way through life.

00:01:27.230 --> 00:01:28.600 align:middle line:90%
And I went to high school.

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:31.960 align:middle line:84%
I managed to somehow
graduate from high school.

00:01:31.960 --> 00:01:34.690 align:middle line:84%
