00:08:21.865 --> 00:08:22.740 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Affirmations.

00:08:22.740 --> 00:08:25.520 align:middle line:84%
>>COTTON: Affirmations,
wonderful goals,

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:28.820 align:middle line:84%
great-life strategies,
positive thinking, but what

00:08:28.820 --> 00:08:33.270 align:middle line:84%
