those thoughts, and goals,

00:08:33.270 --> 00:08:36.929 align:middle line:84%
and affirmations, and
ideas-- if those don't become

00:08:36.929 --> 00:08:38.937 align:middle line:84%
anchored to the
prefrontal cortex,

00:08:38.937 --> 00:08:40.520 align:middle line:84%
to the higher part
of the brain, which

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:42.853 align:middle line:84%
is the part of the brain that
wants to change, and grow,

00:08:42.853 --> 00:08:45.320 align:middle line:84%
